{
  "id": "RAW_35d03f",
  "title": "小型团队实践指南",
  "url": "https://www.latent.space/p/tiny",
  "date": "2025-07-15 19:25:37",
  "author": "Shawn swyx Wang",
  "siteName": "Latent Space",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><em><span>Join our </span><a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://maven.com/p/80aa18/build-your-own-deep-research-with-llamaindex?utm_source%3Dmaven%26utm_medium%3Dics_ll_share_link&amp;sa=D&amp;source=calendar&amp;usd=2&amp;usg=AOvVaw0CqqcgL-DFi1_zD0rxn7Tc\" rel>Build your own Deep Research class</a><span> with Noah and Laurie tomorrow!</span></em></p>\n   <p><span>At the dawn of the </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/s3\" rel>decade of agents</a><span>, AI Engineers and Productivity Agents are combining to create highly efficient teams from the smallest startups to internal skunkworks/</span><a href=\"https://x.com/howietl/status/1937577526634987595\" rel>refounding moments</a><span> at decacorns and publicly listed companies. </span></p>\n   <p><span>I </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/token-data-war\" rel>previously</a><span> defined “</span><strong>Tiny Teams</strong><span>” aspirationally as “</span><strong>teams with more m in ARR than employees”</strong><span>, because </span><strong>efficiency</strong><span> is the ultimate governing force for intellectual (and capital) honesty, </span><em>not</em><span> quantity of tokens or money or lines of code spent vibe coding. It is also a backdoor into a </span><strong>speed</strong><span> discussion, because smaller teams generally move faster, and faster teams generally win. Inter-Human </span><a href=\"https://speedoftrust.com/\" rel>trust</a><span> &amp; I/O is the bottleneck.</span></p>\n   <p><span>The Tiny Teams concept has resonated so strongly that it’s pretty clear it is the next major transition of the org chart as we </span><a href=\"https://the-decoder.com/openai-unveils-five-level-ai-scale-aims-to-reach-level-2-soon/\" rel>go from level 2 to 3 AGI</a><span>. If the </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/ai-engineer\" rel>AI Engineer</a><span> was the single player game, </span><strong><span>Tiny Teams are the co-op multiplayer game</span><span class=\"footnote-hovercard-target\"><a data-component-name=\"FootnoteAnchorToDOM\" id=\"footnote-anchor-1-168403275\" href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/tiny#footnote-1-168403275\" target=\"_self\" rel class=\"footnote-anchor\">1</a></span></strong><span>, capable of far more adaptability, resilience and “damage per second”. Not all players are human.</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!WvlX!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F400fdd18-add9-4ce2-b7d3-84afff23b7b8_1424x796.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/31b82701-8bdf-4087-ba70-9e38b433aa00/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4818b431-9e3e-4a85-6712-707128842d00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75372c1a-5dac-487e-f718-1d9bd9a78f00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/801cbe0d-d25f-4133-09d4-b76be3c7c000/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2dfc3f1d-84d8-4d9d-a8db-67c374b65800/public\" width=\"586\" height=\"327.5674157303371\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/400fdd18-add9-4ce2-b7d3-84afff23b7b8_1424x796.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:796,&quot;width&quot;:1424,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:586,&quot;bytes&quot;:1152610,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/168403275?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F400fdd18-add9-4ce2-b7d3-84afff23b7b8_1424x796.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/70e093c0-e255-47b5-b1d9-7fd90bf04000/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d34983f1-da64-4f23-c090-d9eb1a3e3d00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/33f7ad0f-44c3-4d8d-f7cc-4543fde9a700/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2dfc3f1d-84d8-4d9d-a8db-67c374b65800/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">\n      latent space stickers to whoever can identify the games in the comments\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>The study of </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Organizational_architecture\" rel>org design</a><span> is as old as human civilization, but this is the first time knowledge work can be augmented, automated, and scaled on demand, and organizations that don’t reflect this reality have their head in the sand. </span></p>\n   <p><span>For </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/aiewf-2025-cfp?utm_source=publication-search\" rel>AIEWF</a><span> I curated some of the best examples of Tiny Teams I could find and simply asked them to talk about how they run themselves. We are releasing the full playlist today (which you can find in </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcfpQ4tk2k0WwP1hhmg17j72X-s54AaBu\" rel>YouTube</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/a4faedac-add2-4276-8b59-1cc42e10faa3\" rel>NotebookLM</a><span> format):</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!5veS!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6042c1ea-b724-4d26-a249-380e02499a9c_2454x1512.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc59410b-d34a-4272-0fed-58dcf96dc100/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d5b9505-f64a-41dc-7cb4-52daa7b1fb00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/11cf6902-39ab-4c99-f955-fe3ba37ce900/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2dbdd8e7-3da2-42bf-ee6b-b3f3b235b800/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/93d6180d-2273-47b4-8dc9-d315ca044100/public\" width=\"1456\" height=\"897\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6042c1ea-b724-4d26-a249-380e02499a9c_2454x1512.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:897,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1384753,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/168403275?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6042c1ea-b724-4d26-a249-380e02499a9c_2454x1512.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0fb3ed0-cf0f-46f8-ff13-4c03e1dad800/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9afe2a16-0c5d-4f93-449f-6ea1c4b53f00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2eaf36d0-c530-4fec-c892-4509678aec00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/93d6180d-2273-47b4-8dc9-d315ca044100/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">\n      <span>go to </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcfpQ4tk2k0WwP1hhmg17j72X-s54AaBu\" rel>YouTube now</a><span>! shoutout to Vincent for the great thumbnails</span>\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>Seriously, bookmark the Tiny Teams </span><a href=\"https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/a4faedac-add2-4276-8b59-1cc42e10faa3\" rel>NotebookLM</a><span>! We’ll keep adding to this over time.</span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p><em>Universal advice from 7 teams w/ 100 people &amp; 200m ARR. manually summarized.</em></p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p><strong>Hiring</strong></p>\n     <ul>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Hire right or not at all</strong><span>: </span><em>have</em><span> to be </span><strong>excited</strong><span> about the candidate or it’s a no</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Work Trials</strong><span>: paid projects for 4days-3months to be sure it’s a good fit</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Product-Led Hiring</strong><span>: top customers who quit their jobs to join you</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Top of market salaries</strong><span>: 95th+ percentile salaries</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Small (&lt;15) crew of senior generalists: </strong><span>much fewer juniors</span></p></li>\n     </ul></li>\n    <li>\n     <p><strong>Culture &amp; Value</strong><span>: keep a living culture deck and </span><em>live it</em></p>\n     <ul>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Low ego, high trust</strong><span>: trust = speed, ownership</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Independence, Grit &amp; Resilience</strong><span>: ignore standard VC advice, persevere</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Radical transparency and accountability: </strong><span>wall of work, show &amp; tells</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>User focus</strong><span>: Work closely with users, celebrate them, delight in feedback</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Camaraderie, speed</strong><span>: Have fun, do retreats, avoid burnout</span></p></li>\n     </ul></li>\n    <li>\n     <p><strong>Operations</strong></p>\n     <ul>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Almost no meetings</strong><span>: “deep focus” - building instead of talking about building</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>AI Chief of Staff</strong><span>: automate research, marketing etc w/ </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qw9P1zvCupE&amp;list=PLcfpQ4tk2k0WwP1hhmg17j72X-s54AaBu&amp;index=4&amp;pp=iAQB\" rel>Gumloop</a><span> or </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/lindy\" rel>Lindy</a></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>AI Support</strong><span>: very well fleshed out at this point. e.g. see </span><a href=\"https://www.ycombinator.com/companies/parahelp\" rel>Parahelp</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://blog.railway.com/p/scaling-railway-automating-support\" rel>Railway</a></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Let Fires Burn:</strong><span> in order to prioritize on the 10% critically important</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Compound learning: </strong><span>Oleve phrases it “</span><strong>Don’t Learn It Twice</strong><span>” - build reusable templates and playbooks</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>In Person</strong><span>: either have an office, or </span><strong>VERY</strong><span> frequent AirBnB hack weeks</span></p></li>\n     </ul></li>\n    <li>\n     <p><strong>Tech and Product</strong></p>\n     <ul>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Simple, Boring Tech Stack</strong><span>: shell scripts over k8s, keep code modular.</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Simple Product</strong><span>: start from UI wrapper over one API call to a LLM.</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Feature Flags/Experimentation</strong><span>: one of Oleve’s core principles.</span></p></li>\n      <li>\n       <p><strong>Benchmarks:</strong><span> create top tier internal evals for LLMs/harnesses. Market them.</span></p></li>\n     </ul>\n     <p></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span>(this section is being updated live - if you are reading this on email, this will be updated on the live blog on </span><a href=\"http://Latent.Space\" rel>Latent.Space</a><span>. We’re shipping this out so you can just watch the talks without our commentary, but of course we actually want to absorb the lessons using human attention. Come back in a few days.)</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Gamma: Generalists + Coaches + Culture \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/gamma-generalists-coaches-culture\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>Gamma is one </span><a href=\"https://x.com/patrickc/status/1833648360194265318?s=46\" rel>of the top 25 consumer AI products</a><span> in the world, serving 50 million users with a remarkably lean team of only 30 people. CEO Grant Lee attributes it to three pillars: </span><strong>generalists</strong><span>, </span><strong>player-coaches, </strong><span>and </span><strong>brand/culture </strong><span>of a “small tribe”.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-q8zoXAbmJdI\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;q8zoXAbmJdI&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/q8zoXAbmJdI?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Gumloop: Extreme Hiring, No Meetings, Automate Everything \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/gumloop-extreme-hiring-no-meetings-automate-everything\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>Gumloop was one of the inspirations for Tiny Teams with </span><a href=\"https://x.com/maxbrodeururbas/status/1877778718208446567?s=46\" rel>the stated goal to be a 10-person unicorn</a><span>. CEO Max explains the extreme lengths he goes to to be super picky, from “</span><strong>product led hiring</strong><span>” to </span><strong>4 day work trials</strong><span> all over the world.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-Qw9P1zvCupE\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;Qw9P1zvCupE&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Qw9P1zvCupE?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Bolt.new: Ruthless Prioritization, even with Fires \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/boltnew-ruthless-prioritization-even-with-fires\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>Full disclosure, I am an investor since the Stackblitz days, and we’ve </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=swQLziqWgus&amp;t=370s\" rel>done a podcast with Eric and Itamar</a><span>, but the story of how Bolt kicked off the “AI Builder” category hitting $20m ARR in 60 days with 15 people is very compelling. CEO Eric says </span><em>\"Focusing on 10% of tasks often yields the majority of desired results, forcing clearer thinking.\"</em></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-s8RM8uYxkoY\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;s8RM8uYxkoY&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/s8RM8uYxkoY?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Oleve: Harvesters vs Cultivators \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/oleve-harvesters-vs-cultivators\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>We </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDiEQngFsFU&amp;t=1607s&amp;pp=0gcJCc0JAYcqIYzv\" rel>previously did a lightning pod</a><span> with Sid so we were somewhat familiar with the Oleve story, and, fun fact, since then, this tiny team has launched a THIRD multi million dollar product that will be announced soon. (Consumer product studios operate very stealthily out of necessity). Palantir’s philosophy informs this tiny team.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-pQz-PgA1eJw\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;pQz-PgA1eJw&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:&quot;237s&quot;,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/pQz-PgA1eJw?start=237s&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Hassan El Mghari: Simple but Exciting \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/hassan-el-mghari-simple-but-exciting\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>Together.ai raised eyebrows as it is not “tiny”, but Hassan is classically a one man tiny team, and </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MarPORTD8vo\" rel>no stranger to the AIE stage</a><span>. He now boasts 3m users with a small team.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-gcseUQJ6Gbg\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;gcseUQJ6Gbg&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/gcseUQJ6Gbg?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Datalab: Layoffs = Good \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/datalab-layoffs-good\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>Vik is author of </span><a href=\"https://github.com/datalab-to/marker\" rel>Marker</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://github.com/datalab-to/surya\" rel>Surya</a><span>, but there are many open source vision/pdf/OCR custom models and when I invested it wasn’t obvious how something like this could turn into a profitable company — 7 figure ARR with 7 people, serving tier 1 AI labs. Stretching out the “golden period” of startups where high trust and careful, deliberate hiring of senior generalists dominate is key - per </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qO-YqJm0Q1U&amp;pp=0gcJCc0JAYcqIYzv\" rel>Jeremy Howard</a><span>.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-K-iYKDMFKhE\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;K-iYKDMFKhE&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/K-iYKDMFKhE?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Every: Benchmarks are Memes \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/every-benchmarks-are-memes\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>We think Evals are important, yes, but not enough teams create their own benchmarks to eval models and harnesses to improve their product… and market themselves. Every is “high-taste tester central” and </span><a href=\"https://every.to/on-every/so-we-raised-some-money\" rel>just raised $2m from Reid Hoffman et al</a><span>. Every’s head of AI Practice Alex Duffy talks about how they see benchmarks and launches AI Diplomacy.</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-W3khHzajE04\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;W3khHzajE04&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/W3khHzajE04?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Addendum \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/168403275/addendum\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>There are more Tiny Teams than just the ones we managed to feature of course. Cognition was until recently a team of 80 making well north of $100m, and we’ve been blessed to have Scott Wu come by to tell the story of </span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/T7NWjoD_OuY\" rel>Devin 1.0</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/MI83buT_23o\" rel>Devin 2.0</a><span>. Clearly “Devin 3.0” will involve a </span><a href=\"https://x.com/cognition_labs/status/1944819486538023138\" rel>VSCode Fork</a><span>, as everyone, </span><a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=44560662\" rel>even Amazon</a><span>, has to do in 2025. </span></p>\n   <p><strong>Stay tuned to Latent Space for more Tiny Teams….</strong></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"FootnoteToDOM\" class=\"footnote\">\n    <a id=\"footnote-1-168403275\" href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/tiny#footnote-anchor-1-168403275\" contenteditable=\"false\" target=\"_self\" rel class=\"footnote-number\">1</a>\n    <div class=\"footnote-content\">\n     <p><span>So what would be the “Battle Royale” or “MMO” equivalents? Perhaps this is the next phase </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/noam-brown\" rel>Noam</a><span> is working on.</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文概述了“Tiny Teams”这种组织模式，它利用 AI 和极致效率，助力高绩效的初创公司和企业，并总结了来自多个成功精益团队的实践经验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文概述了“Tiny Teams”这种组织模式，它利用 AI 和极致效率，助力高绩效的初创公司和企业，并总结了来自多个成功精益团队的实践经验。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了“Tiny Teams”的概念——一种通过 AI 工程师和效率工具实现的高效组织，其收入超过员工人数。文章认为，这种模式代表了组织设计的下一个重大转变，即从单人 AI 工程转向协同多人模式。本文的核心内容总结了 Gamma、Gumloop 和 Bolt.new 等七个成功的 Tiny Teams 的通用建议，并将它们的最佳实践归纳为四个方面：招聘（强调以产品为导向的招聘和工作试用）、文化与价值观（注重低 ego、高信任、透明度和用户至上）、运营（尽量减少会议，利用 AI 承担幕僚长和支持角色，并进行严格的优先级排序）以及技术与产品（倡导简单的技术栈、最小可行产品 (MVP) 和强大的内部基准）。本文是对这些团队访谈精选的介绍，旨在为在 AI 时代构建敏捷、有弹性和高影响力的团队提供切实可行的见解。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 赋能的小型团队代表了组织效率和速度的新范式。",
      "explanation": "通过整合 AI 工程师和效率工具，小型团队可以实现不成比例的产出，强调“年度经常性收入（百万美元）超过员工人数”作为衡量成功的标准，并加快迭代周期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Tiny Teams 的成功取决于在招聘、文化、运营和技术等方面的具体、可操作的策略。",
      "explanation": "从严格的招聘流程和高信任文化，到最少的会议和简单的技术栈，这些团队采用反直觉但有效的实践来最大限度地提高产出并最大限度地减少管理开销。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 AI 承担幕僚长和客户支持等运营角色对于扩展精益团队至关重要。",
      "explanation": "AI 自动化使小型团队能够摆脱重复或资源密集型任务，从而使团队成员能够专注于高价值的战略工作和核心产品开发。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "“Tiny Teams”的愿景是“年度经常性收入（百万美元）超过员工人数”，因为效率是智力（和资本）诚实的最终驱动力，而不是代币数量、资金投入或用于营造氛围的代码行数。",
    "如果说 AI 工程师是单人游戏，那么 Tiny Teams 就是协同多人模式，能够实现更强的适应性、弹性和“每秒伤害”。",
    "手动总结了来自 7 个拥有 100 名员工和 2 亿美元年度经常性收入的团队的通用建议。",
    "几乎不开会：“深度专注”——埋头构建，而不是夸夸其谈。",
    "简单、可靠的技术栈：使用 shell 脚本而不是 k8s（Kubernetes），并保持代码模块化。"
  ],
